    take time

## story of the paper
    introduction often lays out the story 
    list out contribution 
    story changes when paper made 

## Quality over Quantity 
## organization is important 
## think like a reader 

No passive, no weased words, no guarantee words, don't belittle the reader 
good figure 
a table of contents paragraph is waste of space.

The details
    a. Relevant , Reviewer? Why relevant 
    b. Replicate experiment 

take the pride in the paper
    a. Contibute to science 
    b. Don't leave your name in the history garbage 
    c. If after 300 years, do you want to associate your name with that paper 

